Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.20,0:38:26.10,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.20,0:38:26.10,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}妈妈已经不在了  生活发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.32,0:38:35.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.32,0:38:35.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}为了生计的我  从早到晚都在劳作
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.91,0:38:44.93,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.91,0:38:44.93,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}村子里的男人们  还是那样地温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:54.23,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.14,0:38:54.23,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}可村里的女人们  却愈发地冷淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.57,0:39:03.54,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.57,0:39:03.54,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}日子虽然清苦  却有浓浓的温情在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.08,0:39:13.13,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.08,0:39:13.13,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}「——相依为命地生活，这就是幸福了吧…」
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:23.08,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.30,0:39:23.08,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}可是为什么…会有这么残酷的事呢…告诉我  神啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.15,0:39:37.77,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.15,0:39:37.77,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}妹妹(那孩子)得赐的  难道不是主送来的  神之御子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:45.98,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:45.98,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}——妹妹怀孕的事情被发现的夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.63,0:39:51.01,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.63,0:39:51.01,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}村里的男人们互相交换着眼色噤口不言
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:56.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.68,0:39:56.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}我听错了吗？打破沉重静寂的是一声脆响
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.63,0:40:00.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.63,0:40:00.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}成衣店的女店主抽在妹妹脸上的耳光声……
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.75,0:40:05.24,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.75,0:40:05.24,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}偷腥的猫…还说什么“可怜的孩子”…这么照顾她…忘恩负义…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.42,0:40:09.47,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.42,0:40:09.47,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}——断片的记忆…判罪的骂声…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:14.45,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:14.45,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…这女的(人)在喊什么？真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.89,0:40:19.56,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.89,0:40:19.56,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}世界剧烈地摇晃着  女店主紧紧揪住我  像是要把我扔出去一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:23.94,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.59,0:40:23.94,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}被染成红色的视野  苦涩的泥土和生锈的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.31,0:40:28.44,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.31,0:40:28.44,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}在头顶起伏的讨论  神父大人愤怒的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.93,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.93,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}纯洁被…与恶魔的契约…灾祸之子种…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.41,0:40:36.07,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.41,0:40:36.07,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}圣母玛利亚…谁都应是加百列…用火焚烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.07,0:40:38.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.07,0:40:38.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}「啊…恶魔不正是你们这些家伙吗！」
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.07,0:40:43.92,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.07,0:40:43.92,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}——然而…妹妹最后只说了一句「谢谢」而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.92,0:40:55.44,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.92,0:40:55.44,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}无情的话语  无情的作为  她受到的伤害难以言表
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:41:06.64,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:41:06.64,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}可即使这样却全都…她真是温柔…全都宽赦了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.34,0:41:11.88,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.34,0:41:11.88,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}「但是、我却绝对不会宽赦啊…」
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:27.28,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:27.28,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}「这个世界毕竟，只是乐园的代用品不是吗。
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.89,0:41:31.86,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.89,0:41:31.86,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}罪孽深重的家伙们全都，一起归于灰烬就好了！」
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.43,0:41:36.75,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.43,0:41:36.75,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}——赤脚的女孩  脸上浮现出寒冰一般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.19,0:41:41.80,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.19,0:41:41.80,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}摇曳的火光  『假面的男人』在它烧灼的黑暗中现出身形——
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.95,0:41:53.72,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.95,0:41:53.72,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}Encore 2:《歓びと哀しみの葡萄酒》
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:57.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:57.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}那是…欢乐地跃动着的“火焰”…悲哀地闪耀着的“宝石”…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:42:02.96,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:42:02.96,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}在许多的生命中…许多的餐桌上…都有她的“葡萄酒”(Vin)——
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.96,0:42:09.17,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.96,0:42:09.17,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}坚持向残暴的命运挑战的女性“Loraine de Saint-Laurant”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:15.47,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.17,0:42:15.47,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}她那与大地一起生活的半生…那不为人知的“故事”(Roman)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.63,0:42:28.88,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.63,0:42:28.88,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…她今天也在田里工作似长实短的“火焰”(光芒)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:42.08,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.88,0:42:42.08,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}无论是得到的还是失去的东西 都经历得太多
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.08,0:42:54.83,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.08,0:42:54.83,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…季节(Saison)多少次地循环流转而不变之物就在此处
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:43:06.50,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.83,0:43:06.50,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}温柔的祖父(Grand-pere)的仆人(Employe) 和所爱的他在一起的“葡萄园”(Clos)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.60,0:43:14.16,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.60,0:43:14.16,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…回忆的时候 是何等甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.16,0:43:23.66,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.16,0:43:23.66,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}像把熟透的果实 摘下来那样快乐(Plaisir)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.22,0:43:46.74,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.22,0:43:46.74,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…将葡萄树(Vigne)那娇嫩的(Delicatesse)小枝剪掉之时 低温而少湿是最为理想
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.74,0:43:59.91,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.74,0:43:59.91,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}种植工们(Vignerons)掐算着早春的日子 主保圣人的节日(St.Vincent)过后就开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.91,0:44:12.73,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.91,0:44:12.73,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…如果对收获(Quantite)过于贪求的话 就会损害它的质量(Qualite)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.73,0:44:24.57,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.73,0:44:24.57,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}一颗(un Grain)…又一颗(et un Grain)… 贯注充分的爱情(Amour)　那是亲人的任务……
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.07,0:44:32.10,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.07,0:44:32.10,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…回忆的时候 是何等苦涩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.10,0:44:38.72,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.10,0:44:38.72,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}像把受伤的果实 摘下来那样痛苦(Peine)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:46.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.09,0:44:46.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…女人不是政治的道具啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:52.76,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:52.76,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}与所爱之人白头偕老的人生(la Vie)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.76,0:44:59.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.76,0:44:59.59,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}再加上…决不会容忍这种事情的贵族(Noble)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.59,0:45:03.98,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.59,0:45:03.98,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}为了将那样的世界(东西)抛弃……
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.14,0:45:08.06,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.14,0:45:08.06,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}(Ah.Ah...Ah.Ah.Ah...)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.06,0:45:08.31,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.06,0:45:08.31,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}“真可惜啊……”
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.73,0:45:20.16,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.73,0:45:20.16,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}满脑都是权威主义的父亲(Pere)… 为了浪费而嫁来的继母(Mere)
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.16,0:45:25.26,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.16,0:45:25.26,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}所谓的名门…开始奢靡的话没落也是相当地快…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:32.91,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:32.91,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}为了把夕阳的斜照挥去…伯爵家(de Comte)… 最后的“王牌”(Carte)…女儿的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.91,0:45:37.35,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.91,0:45:37.35,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}啊…并不知道这只是矫饰的婚礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.35,0:45:41.79,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.35,0:45:41.79,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}继母(女人)的“宝石” 露出了红色(Rouge)的微笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.76,0:46:12.74,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.76,0:46:12.74,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}地平线所讲述的诗歌(声音)… 为了取回重要的东西而…逃跑和斗争的每一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.74,0:46:18.77,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.74,0:46:18.77,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}从那以后，她的人生…已是毫不介意形式的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.74,0:46:34.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.74,0:46:34.55,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}我这一生再也不会爱人 大概也没有去爱的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.55,0:46:58.89,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.55,0:46:58.89,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}但如果谁想润润干渴(Soif)的喉咙 我就会将自己献上…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.56,0:47:26.13,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.56,0:47:26.13,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}在橡木(Chene)桶中　安睡的， 可爱的我的孩子们(ma Enfant)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.13,0:47:37.29,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.13,0:47:37.29,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}喂…你们在做着怎样的梦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.43,0:47:50.00,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.43,0:47:50.00,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}果实的甘甜(Vigne的Sucre) 果皮的苦涩(Tanin的Astringent) 所爱之人留下的，大地的恩惠(Terroir)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.00,0:48:00.76,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.00,0:48:00.76,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}“欢乐”(Joie)与“悲哀”(Chagrin) 交织而成的调和(Harmonie) 那味道就是我的“葡萄酒”(ma "Vin")
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.76,0:48:05.62,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.76,0:48:05.62,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}——而且…那就是“人生”(et C'est "la vie")
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.40,0:48:39.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.40,0:48:39.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}“那里有Roman在吗？”
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:57.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:57.25,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}其れは…歓びに揺らぐ《焔》…哀しみに煌めく《宝石》…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:42:02.96,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.25,0:42:02.96,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}多くの人生…多くの食卓に…彼女の『葡萄酒』(Vin)があった——
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.96,0:42:09.17,my_font,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(100, 100)}
